 <metadata>
  <Title>The Style Guide as an OMDoc Example</Title>
  <Creator role="aut">Michael Kohlhase</Creator> 
  <Date action="created">2002-02-11T0703</Date>
  <Description>
   A discussion of the style guide for OMDoc as an example of an OMDoc text about
   formats. We use it to discuss the basic structure of OMDoc documents.
  </Description>
  <Type>Text</Type>
  <Format>application/omdoc+xml</Format>
</metadata>

<omgroup id="introduction">
 <metadata>
  <Title>Introduction</Title>
 </metadata>
 <omtext id="intro.1">
  <CMP>
   We will use the style guide itself for a discussion of the basic structure of
 <with style="acronym">OMDoc</with> documents. 
  </CMP>
 </omtext>
</omgroup>

