 </omtext>
 
 <omtext id="top-level.ex.3">
  <CMP>
   The root element of the document, it must be <with
    style="omdoc-element">omdoc</with> and it must have an <with
    style="omdoc-attribute">id</with> attribute. Its value can be any string, but
    should not contain ``:'' (this is reserved for namespaces in <with
    style="acronym">xml</with>.<ignore type="ednote">continue</ignore>
  </CMP>
 </omtext>

